ere in the 55+ range what effect your STA has had on your HP. I have a L38 Ogre warrior whos STA is 130. When I created him I maxed his STR and put a few points in STA, AGI, and DEX. Now here is the problem. STR items are a dime a dozen for warriors and I have had little problem getting his STR to 200 but his STA is still REALLY low. When he gets to 55+ how many HP less is he going to have under a warrior whose STA is 200? And does VI calculate your HP increase each level based on your base STA or on your STA with buffs and items? How does all that work? Just wanting to know if I bother to play him all the way up to 60 will I find myself with 250+ STR (50 wasted) and 2K less HP then all the other warriors.<br>
